"meskel square meskel festival\n"
"Meskel : Meskel Festival\n"
"In Addis Ababa, celebrations start in the early afternoon when a procession bearing\n flaming torches approaches Meskal Square from various directions. Thousands gather\n \nat the Square to bid farewell to the rains and welcome in “Tseday” the spring \nseason with its profuse Meskal daisies and golden sunshine."

"meskel festival damera"
"Meskel Meskel Festival"
"As evening darkens, the flames glow brighter. It is not until dawn that the burning pyramid consumes itself entirely and the big tree at the center finally falls. During the celebrations, houses are stocked with tella the local beer, and strangers are made welcome.";
            }
             cout<< "\n\tpress (1) to go back any key to Book: ";
